defaultd risks to the business.  Royal Mail could raise margins further under state ownership
default 
defaultthrough price rises or cost efficiency measures
default as had happened in other EU Member States
default and privatization itself was not necessary to save the business.  Arguments for
default additional capital expenditure (beyond that already funded during the process of the sale) were 
defaultvague
default and 
defaultit was unclear why this could not be funded under state control given that such expenditures have been financed in
default this way
default across the EU.
